com.eiko.back.table

Class CellValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eiko.back.table.CellValue

  • public class CellValue
extends java.lang.Object
    Data holder class for a TableView. I couldn't see a better way of doing this and still be able to have a variable number of attributes. The hash map stores only the attributes that are required for the table while being flexible enough to store any attribute that is needed.
    Version:
    20151211
    Author:
    Melinda Robertson
